en repository is not initialized for later retry\n\n* Remove PII leak in JVM DeviceInfoService by not including username in device model\n\n* Populate TelemetryData fields with real values from device and session context\n\n* Revert \"Fix iOS SDK time-to-first-token to report milliseconds correctly\"\n\nThis reverts commit bd07ca93a4b2841846cb51f1bd57cb59e862e07d.\n\n* Revert iOS-specific changes from host app metadata commit\n\nRemove iOS host app metadata analytics changes to keep only Kotlin changes in this branch\n\n* Update QUICKSTART_ANDROID.md to v0.1.3-alpha with analytics improvements\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Sanchit Monga \u003csanchitmonga22@gmail.com\u003e",
